window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When widowed Amelia Smith takes a fallen soldier into her household, she is shocked to discover he has no idea who he is. Determined to help him recover his memory, she embarks on a journey that will change and endanger them both. </p><p>Working out whom and what he is brings back painful memories to Marco. The only constant in his life is his burning desire to take revenge on those who tried to steal everything from him. As his memories return, he needs Amelia Smith's calm good sense more than he ever anticipated. Can a relationship begun in such an unorthodox fashion blossom into love? Especially when the lady is hiding secrets of her own. </p>"; 
